Quickscreen is the quick way to set up your display layout!

To use it, add a keybinding under 

'Settings -> All -> Input -> Key Bindings' - 'Quickscreen -> Show Quickscreen Popup'

You can also find a 'none popup' version under 
'Settings -> All -> Extensions' -> 'Quickscreen'

Find help on irc.freenode.net #e.de
